  "name": "RPlog_Face_Off",
  "title": "A New Face Under the Cover of Darkness",
  "summary": "Aboard the Hyperion docked at Mos Eisley, former Moff Bailey Laran summons the arms dealer Tritus and his Verpine doctor Madixli for a clandestine job: surgically altering a sedated man's appearance to perfectly match a holo-image, scar and all, for an unnamed spy operation. Tritus, ever wary, presses for payment and warns Bailey against any treachery even as she boasts of her hundreds of soldiers and forming naval fleet. While Madixli works its meticulous, permanent transformation, Bailey and Tritus trade barbed banter over glasses of water, watched silently by Tritus's bodyguards Tal'sin and Vaughan. The Verpine completes the flawless surgery, Bailey inspects and approves the result, and pays out 2600 freshly earned credits. The night's work done, Tritus and his doctor depart the ship.",
